# Umrah Journey Guide

Welcome to Umrah Journey Guide, a resource dedicated to helping pilgrims prepare for a smooth and meaningful Umrah journey.

## About

This repository shares useful information, travel tips, and planning resources for individuals and families preparing for Umrah from the UAE and other regions.

## Topics Covered

- Umrah travel checklists
- Visa preparation guidance
- Packing essentials for pilgrims
- Makkah and Madinah travel tips
- Accommodation considerations
- Ihram guidelines and preparations
- Family Umrah travel advice
- Common mistakes to avoid during Umrah

## Purpose

The goal of this project is to provide practical and easy-to-understand information that helps pilgrims focus on their spiritual journey with confidence and peace of mind.

